# NEVER commit the private signing key.
# Only the public key (public_key.pem) ships in the product.
# Generate the production keypair offline and store it only on the license server.
#   openssl genpkey -algorithm Ed25519 -out private_key.pem
#   openssl pkey -in private_key.pem -pubout -out public_key.pem
private_key.pem
*.key
